    "## 8. Summary\n",
    "\n",
    "### What we've built:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. ✅ Complete Mamba Language Model\n",
    "2. ✅ Token embeddings with weight tying\n",
    "3. ✅ Stacked Mamba blocks\n",
    "4. ✅ Language model head\n",
    "5. ✅ Text generation\n",
    "\n",
    "### Training observations:\n",
    "\n",
    "- Loss decreases over training\n",
    "1.  The model learns character-level patterns\n",
